snippet.title: Amber Heard did not donate 7 million to charity// Proof is finally released // #justiceforjohnny
snippet.description:
We now have legal proof that Amber Heard did not donate the 7 million dollars to charity. Instead pledged and told the public and media she did while lying under oath. It is no longer a question but instead answered.

Judge Nichol even tried to use this 7 million donation as a reason why he believed her. Well, she didn't donate as stated countless times. There's just no way she can spin this. She lied under oath when she said she donated money.

She said she donated the 7 million...end of story. Instead, she has kept 7 million since 2018. How many more lies will surface with legal proof?

Hey sign this petition: https://www.change.org/p/dc-entertainment-remove-amber-heard-from-aquaman-2

Personal blog: afriendorfoe.homeblog
